g.text: College of Engineering and Information Technology
Welcome to the Department of Information Systems at UMBC. Our interdisciplinary program helps students develop in demand skills,
preparing them for careers in IT and IS. Located near technology hubs, our suburban campus is an exciting place to be for students
in tech. With a variety of degree programs to choose from, we offer programs designed to give you options for applying information
systems to your career. To learn more, please contact us with any questions.
